    "description": "This small stir fry packs a punch. You'll pan fry carrot, sweet pea pods and prawns in an umami-loaded gochujang sauce before serving with brown rice on the side. Smaller portion providing 2 of your 5-a-day, a source of fibre and high in protein.",
